description: These brownies are based on ground Brazil nuts, serve with dark chocolate.
name: Brazil Nut Brownies Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Leave the brownie to cool completely before peeling off the greaseproof paper and slicing. To serve, dust with cacao powder and a little matcha powder, infusion.
